FBIS4-62275 "drsov093_d_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-093 Daily Report 12 May 1994 Regional Affairs Chuvashia To Become Tax Free Zone for 3 Years Chuvashia To Become Tax Free Zone for 3 Years LD1205163294 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 1100 GMT 12 May 94 LD1205163294 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy Russian BFN [Text] Chuvashia is to become a taxfree zone for three years. In accordance with an edict issued by republican President Fedorov, all enterprises and organizations which produce consumer goods and technical equipment will be exempt from income tax. Banks and insurance companies will also pay lower taxes.
